Subject: Unsupportet program
Description:
Hi,
we use the pingcastle 3.3.0.1 for auditing.
Today i downloaded version 3.3.0.11 with the same license key.
When i start the software, i got the message "The program is unsupportet since: 2025-05-17 00:00:00Z).

Christian
Solution_Comment__c: License was not propogating when downloading PingCastle version 3.3.0.11. After updating the application using the auto-updater, the issue was resolved.
